thread.title: James

author: James
title: James
text: Could have fallen asleep from the lack of drama when I ordered a sink disposal from them. From ordering to delivery, everything went so smoothly, I had to make sure I wasn't wearing my PJs because I thought I was dreaming. This is what ordering kitchen equipment is supposed to be like. The disposal went in easily, as did the control panel. Customer is pleased, I got paid. Life is good.
